String fragment Fragment component or {@code null} for none.
List<String> pathParts Decoded path component by parts with each part separated by a {@code '/'} or {@code null} for none, for example {@code "/m8/feeds/contacts/default/full"} is represented by {@code "", "m8", "feeds", "contacts", "default", "full"}.
